info.author: Denis Stalz-John
classifiers: Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.name: niceml
info.summary: Welcome to niceML 🍦, a Python-based MLOps framework that uses TensorFlow and Dagster. This framework streamlines the development, and maintenance of machine learning models, providing an end-to-end solution for building efficient and scalable pipelines.
